.env.example additions: # Container-internal artifact paths DATA_DIR=/app/data CHECKPOINT_DIR=/app/checkpoints LOGS_DIR=/app/logs SPLITS_DIR=/app/configs/splits # HPO POSTGRES_DB_OPTUNA=optuna OPTUNA_STORAGE_URL= REPLICA_INDEX=0 # Logging PREFECT_LOGGING_EXTRA_LOGGERS=minivess
In Dockerfile.train: DELETE lines like `ENV DATA_DIR=/app/data` — add comment: # DATA_DIR, CHECKPOINT_DIR, LOGS_DIR, SPLITS_DIR are injected by docker-compose # from .env.example. Do NOT hardcode them here (CLAUDE.md Rule #22).
In docker-compose.flows.yml x-common-env: add DATA_DIR: ${DATA_DIR:-/app/data} CHECKPOINT_DIR: ${CHECKPOINT_DIR:-/app/checkpoints} LOGS_DIR: ${LOGS_DIR:-/app/logs} SPLITS_DIR: ${SPLITS_DIR:-/app/configs/splits} PREFECT_LOGGING_EXTRA_LOGGERS: ${PREFECT_LOGGING_EXTRA_LOGGERS:-minivess}
